    {
      "para_id": "Q000945.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanna , the firstborn child of Enlil , his master , Ur-Namma , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , the builder of Nanna’s temple , restored the ancient state of affairs : he let the sea merchants reach the quay walls on the seashore , and returned the Magan boats under ( Nanna’s ) authority ."
    }
  ],
